OL,3,CGovernment announce support hub to
OL,4,Chelp those affected by terror attacks
OL,6,FGranada's Victoria Grimes joined
OL,7,Fsurvivors at the meeting in
OL,8,FWestminster.
OL,10,FThe Government has announced new
OL,11,Fmeasures to support victims of
OL,12,Fterrorism, including the introduction
OL,13,Fof a new National Day.
OL,15,FThe "Plan for Change" from the
OL,16,FGovernment hopes to meet the needs of
OL,17,Fthose affected by terrorist attacks,
OL,18,Fsuch as the 2017 Manchester Arena
OL,19,Fattack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
