OL,3,CGovernment announce support hub to
OL,4,Chelp those affected by terror attacks
OL,6,FDr Cath Hill survived the Arena attack
OL,7,Falong with her 10-year-old son, and
OL,8,Fsays support for young people is long
OL,9,Foverdue.
OL,11,FShe said: "I wholeheartedly welcome
OL,12,Fthis news. Sadly, we know as a society
OL,13,Fwe are not immune from future terror
OL,14,Fattacks; therefore, it is essential
OL,15,Fthat future survivors get the help and
OL,16,Fsupport they need.
OL,18,F"If we are to combat the devastation
OL,19,Fthat terrorism can cause, as a society
OL,20,Fwe must care for those who bear the
OL,21,Fbrunt of these acts of terror. "
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
