OL,3,CGovernment announce support hub to
OL,4,Chelp those affected by terror attacks
OL,6,FThe Government has announced an
OL,7,Fofficial support hub for terror
OL,8,Fvictims and survivors, where they can
OL,9,Freceive help and advice as they deal
OL,10,Fwith the immediate and long-term
OL,11,Faftermath of terrorist attacks.
OL,13,FSecurity Minister Dan Jarvis said:
OL,14,F"The impact of a terrorist attack is
OL,15,Flong-lasting and evolving. Victims and
OL,16,Fsurvivors of terrorism need the
OL,17,Fhighest levels of support to recover
OL,18,Fand rebuild their lives. These reforms
OL,19,Fwill significantly enhance the support
OL,20,Favailable to those affected.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
