OL,3,CGovernment announce support hub to
OL,4,Chelp those affected by terror attacks
OL,6,FConsultation has also begun on a new
OL,7,Fnational day for victims and survivors
OL,8,Fof terrorism, which it's hoped will
OL,9,Fhelp the country to remember and
OL,10,Fhonour those who have been killed or
OL,11,Fimpacted by terrorist attacks.
OL,13,FTravis Frain, from Blackburn, broke
OL,14,Fnearly every bone in his body when he
OL,15,Fwas injured in the Westminster Bridge
OL,16,FTerror Attack in 2017 which killed
OL,17,Ffive people.
OL,19,FSince the attack, Travis has been
OL,20,Fcampaigning for a national day for
OL,21,Fterrorism survivors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
