OL,6,FHe said: "This is something that I,
OL,7,Fand several other survivors, have been
OL,8,Fcampaigning on for many years, and I'm
OL,9,Fpleased to see that this government
OL,10,Frecognises the importance of these
OL,11,Fissues and the role that they can play
OL,12,Fin facilitating the recovery of those
OL,13,Fimpacted by horrific acts of terrorism.
OL,15,F"Hundreds of survivors don't feel they
OL,16,Fhave a voice, so it's important we get
OL,17,Fout there and speak for them whenever
OL,18,Fwe can."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
