OL,6,FBefore the day is officially
OL,7,Frecognised, the Government has
OL,8,Flaunched a consultation to allow
OL,9,Fvictims and members of the public to
OL,10,Fprovide their input.
OL,12,FDan Jarvis said: "We think it's right
OL,13,Fthat there is a focal point in the
OL,14,Fyear... to reflect on those we have
OL,15,Flost to terrorism.
OL,17,F"I'm really pleased we're on the road
OL,18,Fto doing it properly... The purpose of
OL,19,Fthe consultation is to think about how
OL,20,Fbest to do it."
